    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　栁州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:226'>　國風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:230'>柏舟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='230:253'>　魯詩劉向曰衛宣夫人齊侯之女也嫁於衛至城門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='253:276'>　而衛君死女遂入持三年之喪畢弟立請曰衛小國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='276:299'>　也不容二庖願請同廬衛君使人愬於齊之兄弟齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='299:325'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='325:348'>　兄弟皆欲之女终不聴而作詩曰我心匪石不可轉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='348:371'>　也我心匪席不可卷也厄窮而不憫榮辱而不苟然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='371:394'>　後能自致也言不失也然後可以濟難也詩曰威儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='394:417'>　逮逮不可選也言其左右無賢臣皆順其君之欲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='417:438'>　<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span>　李适仲曰衛宣姜自誓而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='438:461'>　　此所謂宣姜宣公皆誤左傳宣公納伋之妻為宣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='461:484'>　　姜未聞其後更娶齊女至城門而公死為公守節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='484:507'>　　持喪且宣公之子惠公繼立為君並無弟繼為君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='507:533'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='533:556'>　　之事或别是一人而非宣姜且是引詩之人非作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='556:579'>　　詩之人要不足深辨也　説苑引憂心悄悄二句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='579:607'>　　曰小人成羣斯足憂矣又同毛序未知何故<span class='krp-note'>向治/魯詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='607:641'>　　<span class='krp-note'>其子歆好毛詩左傳執以問向向往/往不能難是劉氏固兼通毛詩矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='641:651'>威儀棣棣不可選也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='651:673'>　魯詩賈誼曰棣棣富也不可選衆也<span class='krp-note'>容/經</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='673:696'>　　左傳北宫子引此二句言君臣上下内外大小皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='696:717'>　　有威儀也毛傳物有其容不可數也義俱同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='717:743'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='743:749'>胡迭而微</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='749:767'>　韓詩迭作臷傳曰臷常也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='767:790'>　　胡常而微言日月至明胡常有時而微不照見我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='790:798'>　　之憂思也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='798:802'>燕燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='802:825'>　魯詩劉向曰衛定姜者定公之夫人公子之母也公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='825:848'>　子旣娶而死其婦無子畢三年之喪定姜歸其婦自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='848:871'>　送之至于魯乃賦詩曰燕燕于飛差池其羽之子于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='871:897'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='897:920'>　歸遠送于野送去歸泣而望之又作詩曰先君之思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='920:947'>　以朂寡人君子以定姜為慈姑<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span>鄭氏曰定姜無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='947:970'>　子立庶子衎是為獻公畜孝公也獻公無禮于定姜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='970:1012'>　定姜作此詩<span class='krp-note'>禮記注師鄭志答炅模曰為記注時就/盧君先  亦然後乃得毛公傳記古書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1012:1059'>　<span class='krp-note'>義又且然記注已行不復改之也按盧君即盧植與/鄭共師馬融其云先師即馬融  融注列女傳皆魯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1059:1082'>　<span class='krp-note'>詩/説</span>　李适仲曰衛定姜歸其娣送之而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1082:1105'>　　毛傳作莊姜送戴媯魯乃作定姜送婦或傳之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1105:1126'>　　自也但詩文不類送婦且非持喪大歸之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1126:1152'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1152:1162'>先君之思以朂寡人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1162:1189'>　魯詩鄭氏曰言獻公當思先君定公以孝于寡人<span class='krp-note'>禮/記</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1189:1196'>　<span class='krp-note'>注/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1196:1211'>　　獻公無禮于定姜事見左傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1211:1215'>日月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1215:1221'>報我不述</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1221:1235'>　韓詩述作術薛君曰術法也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1235:1239'>終風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1239:1265'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1265:1281'>終風且暴　謔浪笑傲　曀曀其隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1281:1308'>　韓詩終風西風也謔起也　曀作㙪天隂塵也<span class='krp-note'>俱釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1308:1312'>擊鼓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1312:1318'>死生契濶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1318:1333'>　韓詩契濶約束也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1333:1356'>　　毛以契濶為勤苦不如韓長正義曰五人為伍謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1356:1379'>　　與其伍中之人相約束也軍法有兩卒師旅其約</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1379:1402'>　　亦可相及獨言伍者以執手相約必與親近左傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1402:1428'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1428:1451'>　　曰不死伍乗軍之大刑也是同伍相救故舉以言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1451:1456'>　　之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1456:1462'>于嗟洵兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1462:1479'>　韓詩吁嗟敻兮敻遠也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1479:1502'>　　毛傳釋洵為遠謂軍伍之疏遠也韓作夐遠似嘆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1502:1515'>　　南行師期之遠亦可通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1515:1519'>凱風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1519:1539'>　魯詩趙岐孟子注莫慰母心謂母心不悦也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1539:1565'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1565:1588'>　　大戴記曾子曰有子七人莫慰母心子之辭也孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1588:1611'>　　子曰凱風親之過小者也曰子之辭曰過小則非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1611:1634'>　　不安其室之意葢七子未嘗不能慰其母心而母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1634:1657'>　　不悦其子有心苛虐七子反而自責故曰莫慰也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1657:1680'>　　母不過少慈恩是謂過小且非母之自言是謂子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1680:1703'>　　之辭趙注所以止作母心不悦而不及其他若不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1703:1721'>　　安其室義将與父絶而猶曰過小乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1721:1725'>雄雉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1725:1751'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1751:1761'>不忮不求何用不臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1761:1784'>　魯詩馬融曰言不忮害不貪求何用為不善乎疾貪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1784:1798'>　惡忮害之詞<span class='krp-note'>論語/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1798:1821'>　韓詩外傳曰夫利為害本禍為福先唯不求利者為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1821:1836'>　無禍故曰不忮不求何用不臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1836:1859'>　　馬融以為疾貪惡忮害之詩前三章若無可見葢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1859:1882'>　　篇終始露本意也韓以不求福利為善義亦相同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1882:1894'>　　皆非刺淫與毛序異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1894:1920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1920:1926'>匏有苦葉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1926:1934'>深則厲淺則揭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1934:1948'>　韓詩至心曰厲<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1948:1971'>　　厲説文作砅履石渡也毛傳以衣渉水鄭注論語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1971:1985'>　　由膝以上為厲義各不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1985:1991'>招招舟子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1991:2005'>　韓詩招招聲也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2005:2025'>　　毛曰號召貌王逸曰以口曰召以手曰招</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2025:2051'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2051:2055'>谷風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2055:2073'>采葑采菲無以下體徳音莫違及爾同死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2073:2096'>　魯詩鄭氏曰此詩故親今疎也言人之交當如采葑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2096:2119'>　采菲取一善而已君子無求備于一人能如此則徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2119:2142'>　音之美不離令名我願與之同死矣<span class='krp-note'>禮記/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2142:2165'>　　此雖以詩文釋引詩斷章取義之意然曰故親今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2165:2185'>　　疎曰言人之交似不指棄婦而指朋友也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2185:2203'>行道遲遲中心有違不遠伊邇薄送我畿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2203:2229'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2229:2256'>　韓詩違狠也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　白虎通出婦之義必送之接以賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2256:2268'>　客之禮故曰薄送我畿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2268:2279'>毋發我笱　有洸有潰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2279:2297'>　韓詩發亂也潰不善之貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2297:2301'>式微</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2301:2324'>　魯詩劉向曰黎莊夫人者衛侯之女旣往而不同欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2324:2347'>　未嘗得見其傅母閔夫人賢公反不納恐其見遺而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2347:2370'>　不以時去乃作詩曰式微式微胡不歸夫人曰彼雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2370:2396'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2396:2419'>　不吾以吾可以離于婦道乎乃作詩曰微君之故胡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2419:2446'>　為乎中露<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span>劉歆曰黎莊夫人執行不衰莊公不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2446:2469'>　偶行節反乖傅母勸去作詩式微夫人守節終不肯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2469:2478'>　歸<span class='krp-note'>傳/贊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2478:2502'>　　魯詩所𫝊事必有本但考左傳晉滅赤潞氏數之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2502:2525'>　　以奪黎地未聞黎莊有失徳也泥中中露皆衛地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2525:2540'>　　毛傳以為失國而寓之更明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2540:2544'>簡兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2544:2570'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2570:2581'>碩人俁俁　右手秉翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2581:2604'>　韓詩俁作扈傳曰扈扈美貌又曰萬以夷翟大鳥羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2604:2612'>　<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2612:2635'>　　正義曰公羊説樂萬舞以鴻羽取其勁翮一舉千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2635:2657'>　　里爾雅翟雉属皆非夷翟大鳥韓葢别有所本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2657:2661'>泉水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2661:2672'>毖彼泉水　飲餞于禰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2672:2701'>　韓詩毖作祕<span class='krp-note'>篇海璧吉/切刺也</span>禰作坭傳曰送行飲酒曰餞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2701:2727'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2727:2735'>　<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2735:2739'>北門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2739:2752'>王事敦我　室人交徧摧我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2752:2779'>　韓詩摧作䜅<span class='krp-note'>以追/反</span>傳曰敦迫也䜅就也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2779:2792'>　　按就者就而叢責之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2792:2796'>靜女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2796:2807'>靜女其姝　搔首踟蹰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2807:2838'>　韓詩傳曰靜貞也躊躇<span class='krp-note'>原/文</span>躑躅也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　外傳曰賢者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2838:2864'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2864:2887'>　精氣闐溢而後傷時不可過也乃陳情欲以歌道義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2887:2904'>　詩曰愛而不見搔首躊躇急時辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2904:2927'>　　内傳以靜女為貞女外傳以為賢者急時之辭而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2927:2943'>　　曰歌道義皆與取彤管之意合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2943:2947'>新臺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2947:2967'>燕婉之求臺新臺有洒河水浼浼　得此戚施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2967:2990'>　韓詩燕作嬿洒作漼浼作浘傳曰漼鮮貌浘浘盛貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2990:3015'>　<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>薛君曰戚施蟾蜍喻醜惡<span class='krp-note'>太平/御覧</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3015:3041'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3041:3069'>　　戚施説文作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1434' title='KR1434' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1434.png'/>蠒蟾蜍類形醜又不能仰也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3069:3075'>二子乗舟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3075:3098'>　魯詩劉向曰衛宣公之子伋也壽也伋前妻之子也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3098:3121'>　壽母與朔謀欲殺之而立壽使人與伋乗舟于河中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3121:3144'>　将沈而殺之壽知不能止也因與之同舟舟人不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3144:3167'>　殺伋方乗舟時伋傅母恐其死也閔而作詩舟行無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3167:3190'>　恙未㡬又使伋之齊使盗見載旌者要而殺之壽止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3190:3213'>　伋伋不可壽又與之偕行壽之母知之戒之曰壽無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3213:3240'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-10a' );" name="004-10a" class="pb">[004-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3240:3263'>　為前也壽又竊伋旌以先行幾至齊矣盜見旌而殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3263:3287'>　之伋至痛弟代己遂載其尸還至境自殺<span class='krp-note'>新/序</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3287:3310'>　　新序之勝於毛傳者有三以伋為前妻所生之子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3310:3334'>　　則知伋為宣公為世子時所生非烝于夷姜而生者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3334:3357'>　　及其即位年已長大故可立為太子一也姜與朔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3357:3380'>　　共謀殺伋其事秘國人何由知而賦詩若傅母在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3380:3403'>　　内又知而不敢言也是以閔而作詩二也姜欲壽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3403:3426'>　　為太子愛之也壽之先與伋共舟所以阻其沈舟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3426:3453'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-10b' );" name="004-10b" class="pb">[004-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3453:3476'>　　之謀尚非代死代死在竊旌耳其後壽死于盜伋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3476:3499'>　　雖至不敢再殺乃載尸還境痛弟之代己以自戕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3499:3523'>　　情事宛然三也三家雖多雜出而𫝊之有自學者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3523:3535'>　　亦信其所可信而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3535:3539'>柏舟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3539:3545'>實維我特</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3545:3564'>　韓詩特作直傳曰相當值也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3564:3587'>　　言共姜撫兹藐孤而愴心曰髧彼両髦實我相當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3587:3614'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-11a' );" name="004-11a" class="pb">[004-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3614:3637'>　　值以撫飬之也共伯為武公之兄史稱武公弑而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3637:3660'>　　自立是未可信但共伯旣已嗣位則非幼小可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3660:3683'>　　毛傳亦属未當兩髦自是共伯遺孤韓云當值猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3683:3693'>　　云遭此閔凶耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3693:3698'>墻有茨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3698:3709'>中冓之言　不可詳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3709:3730'>　魯故冓作㝤故曰中㝤中夜也<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3730:3757'>　韓詩中冓中夜謂淫僻之言也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　詳作揚傳曰揚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3757:3784'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-11b' );" name="004-11b" class="pb">[004-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3784:3795'>　猶道也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3795:3818'>　　周禮媒氏注隂訟争中冓之事聴之亡國之社葢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3818:3841'>　　掩其上而棧其下使無所通就之以聴隂訟之情</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3841:3861'>　　明不當宣露是冓為構合之義毛傳為長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3861:3867'>君子偕老</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3867:3878'>委委佗佗　邦之媛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3878:3905'>　韓詩佗作他傳曰他他徳之美貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　媛作援傳曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3905:3911'>　援取也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3911:3938'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-12a' );" name="004-12a" class="pb">[004-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3938:3961'>　　佗佗為徳之美即平易之謂與毛傳同不如從正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3961:3984'>　　義作行歩之美為是援之訓取言為邦人之取法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3984:3989'>　　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3989:3995'>鶉之奔奔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3995:4027'>鶉之奔奔<span class='krp-note'>記作/賁賁</span>鵲之彊彊<span class='krp-note'>記作/姜姜</span>人之無良我以為君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4027:4050'>　魯詩鄭氏曰賁賁姜姜争闘惡貌良善也言我以惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4050:4073'>　人為君亦使我惡如大鳥姜姜於上小鳥賁賁於下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4073:4082'>　<span class='krp-note'>禮記/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4082:4109'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-12b' );" name="004-12b" class="pb">[004-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4109:4127'>　韓詩賁賁彊彊乗匹之貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4127:4150'>　　賁賁彊彊毛傳無解集傳以為非匹偶而相從依</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4150:4173'>　　韓説也魯但云以惡人為君意鶉好闘鵲性燥皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4173:4194'>　　非淫鳥故以争闘取義耳然不如從韓為長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4194:4197'>定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4197:4211'>　魯詩仲梁子曰初立楚宫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4211:4234'>　　鄭志答張逸曰仲梁先師魯人當六國時在毛公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4234:4258'>　　前按韓非子八儒有仲良氏之儒陶潛羣輔録有仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4258:4285'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-13a' );" name="004-13a" class="pb">[004-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4285:4308'>　　梁傳樂為道語葢先申公浮邱伯而説詩者先儒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4308:4317'>　　皆定為魯詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4317:4323'>星言夙駕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4323:4336'>　韓詩星精也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4336:4340'>蝃蝀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4340:4363'>　韓序蝃蝀刺奔女也詩人言蝃蝀在東者邪色乗陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4363:4386'>　人君淫佚之徴臣子為君父隱藏故言莫之敢指也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4386:4396'>　<span class='krp-note'>後漢/書注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4396:4423'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-13b' );" name="004-13b" class="pb">[004-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4423:4446'>　　如韓説是刺宣姜之詩也毛作衛文有道國人不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4446:4457'>　　齒淫奔與韓不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4457:4461'>相鼠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4461:4484'>　三家詩妻得諫夫者夫婦榮恥共之此妻諫夫之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4484:4501'>　也妻諫夫不知何指白乕通多雜出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4501:4505'>干旄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4505:4515'>彼妹者子何以予之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4515:4543'>　韓詩傳曰譬猶練絲染之藍則青染之朱則赤<span class='krp-note'>王充/論衡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4543:4570'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-14a' );" name="004-14a" class="pb">[004-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4570:4580'>　<span class='krp-note'>引詩/述傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4580:4603'>　　按左傳竿旄何以告之取其忠也家語曰干旄之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4603:4626'>　　忠告至矣哉皆取姝子忠告善道之意此以素絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4626:4639'>　　染練為喻正善道之謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4639:4643'>載馳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4643:4666'>　魯詩劉向曰許穆夫人者衛懿公之女初許求之齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4666:4689'>　亦求之懿公将與許女因其傅母言曰舎近而就遠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4689:4712'>　離大而附小一旦有車馳之難孰可與慮社稷衛君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4712:4739'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-14b' );" name="004-14b" class="pb">[004-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4739:4762'>　不聴其後狄人攻衛破之許不能救夫人馳驅而弔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4762:4779'>　衛侯因疾之而作詩<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4779:4802'>　　劉以許穆夫人為懿公之女誤也按左傳齊人使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4802:4825'>　　昭伯烝于宣姜生文公齊子宋桓夫人許穆夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4825:4848'>　　其事雖屬可疑但懿公為惠公之子是宣公之孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4848:4871'>　　也宋桓夫人與許穆夫人與惠公為兄弟而懿公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4871:4894'>　　乃其侄耳即如左傳夫人為昭伯所生亦是姊行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4894:4917'>　　豈懿公所生之女乎夫人之唁衛侯為宗社淪亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4917:4944'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-15a' );" name="004-15a" class="pb">[004-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4944:4967'>　　唁其兄弟故許人以義訧之而夫人终不得往也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4967:4990'>　　　左氏謂夫人之唁衛在戴公時是據詩文言至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4990:5013'>　　于漕為説也亦悞狄入衛在閔公之二年冬十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5013:5036'>　　月宋桓公隨立戴公以廬于漕而是年戴公隨卒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5036:5059'>　　文公嗣立是戴之立止一月耳周之十二月夏之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5059:5082'>　　十月詩云芃芃其麥言采其蝱豈十月途中之景</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5082:5105'>　　乎葢唁衛當在衛之初滅或文公之時也　左傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5105:5128'>　　載叔孫豹賦馳之四章取控于大邦誰因誰極之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5128:5155'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-15b' );" name="004-15b" class="pb">[004-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5155:5178'>　　意似可為夫人先請其父欲與齊以為外援之証</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5178:5200'>　　即韓傳亦如魯詩所傳也但父為宣公非懿公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5200:5223'>　韓詩外傳高子問於孟子曰夫嫁娶者非己所自親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5223:5247'>　也衛女何以得編于詩也孟子曰有衛女之志則可無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5247:5270'>　衛女之志則怠夫道二常謂之經變謂之權夫衛女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5270:5283'>　行中孝慮中聖權如之何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5283:5306'>　　按外傳連公孫丑問伊尹放太甲為一章或是孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5306:5324'>　　子軼文流傳于後者與列女傳正同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5324:5351'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '004-16a' );" name="004-16a" class="pb">[004-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5351:5362'>大夫跋渉　許人尤之</span><br/>
